{"tid":1269119,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家唔好再鋪天蓋地散播自殺詳細資訊","createTime":"2019-06-30T13:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T13:57:48.000Z","uid":114951,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"989c04aa9bdc1e38eeeb2846df9866dc17cb2c27","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:02:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢幾日好多負面消息<br />\n但係咁多位手足要一齊頂住<br />\n唔開心搵我/搵朋友/搵社工傾<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一個都不能再少</span></span><br />\n另外，係連登同各大社交媒體<br />\n麻煩想傳相關資訊嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">簡單講重點即可<br />\n唔好大篇幅詳細講哂所有資料<br />\n唔好合理化自殺行為</span></span><br />\n要記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做傻事解決唔到問題</span><br />\n跟住嘅路要齊齊整整行落去<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日7.1出黎遊行!</span><br />\n<br />\nquote: <br />\n世衛組織建議報導媒體報導自殺新聞的原則：<br />\n<br />\n「六要」與「六不」<br />\n「六不」：<br />\n．不要刊登出照片或自殺遺書。<br />\n．不要報導自殺方式的細節。<br />\n．不要簡化自殺的原因。<br />\n．不要將自殺光榮化或聳動化。<br />\n．不要使用宗教或文化的刻板印象來解讀。<br />\n．不要過度責備。<br />\n「六要」：<br />\n．當報導事件時，與醫療衛生專家密切討論。<br />\n．提到自殺時，用「自殺身亡」而不要用「自殺成功」這樣的字眼。<br />\n．只報導相關的資訊，且刊登在內頁而非頭版。<br />\n．凸顯不用自殺的其他解決方法。<br />\n．提供與自殺防治有關的求助專線與社區資源。<br />\n．報導危險指標以及可能的警訊徵兆。<br />\nsource <br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%BE%9E1991%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E6%BD%AE%E8%AA%AA%E8%B5%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25BE%259E1991%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E8%25B5%25B7%2F&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXCYtkWzW%2FBkyQE6eFpzr100%3D&h=488bbc54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25BE%259E1991%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E8%25B5%25B7%2F&h=45499c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%BE%9E1991%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA%E6%BD%AE%E8%AA%AA%E8%B5%B7/</a><br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n生命熱線：2382 0000<br />\n撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：2389 2222<br />\n社會福利署：2343 2255<br />\n明愛向晴軒：18288"},{"pid":"a93baa00b74ac0b9e5d264d03b1a988a502d5ca4","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc06c1b0925aa9566af7bedcb7c8573ee6e6e1b7","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0adb9f090225dd65b5e910345452fbfc04fd687","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:05:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfced83ece1d623298208d7b8134b2b78668612a","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"唔好再有手足做傻事啦"},{"pid":"2beed8a059423008eb044b2881ccddcd2bbd5264","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:07:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3988f3c4678dbeffe5a5c1950c2e899e7188b23f","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"今晚+聽日攰都要行出黎<br />\n為左烈士，為左自己，為左我地鐘意嘅香港"},{"pid":"28017f5e3be337fa682112a22e4b65e398412cad","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"6ef179b39163aebf215c690fdbe58498c78e7e30","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a089247720851b01d42ef16f2fe127374816fd8e","tid":1269119,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士少少意見<br />\n<br />\n第一件事係要有可靠渠道等D情緒受困擾既手足尋求協助,乜野叫可靠係講緊聆聽者係唔會篤灰.而求助人亦要盡量唔好隨便提一D會令自身有被控風險既事.若果真係要講就清搵d可靠既人去講<br />\n<br />\n第二件事想自殺既手足要明白,其實你都係其他手足之中一個好重要既精神支柱.若果你選擇自殺離去.某程度上即係掉低d手足唔理姐.何況你既死對於當權都只係一件好少既事.你認為佢地會為左年輕人既死就會得到反醒?太天真啦.<br />\n<br />\n第三件事我地會覺得有手足選擇離去感到可惜,但係請想死既你唔好諗住死左就係烈士.如期一死,不如好好利用自己既選票,能力去嘗試改變一下個社會.真係改變唔到就逃出香港吧.總好過未嘗過美好風光就為左依個垃圾政府而死吧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要.你係每一個同路人既精神支柱.依個時勢大家既精神係唔可以散.<br />\n若果又多一個死.即係又少個同路人.同埋或許會有骨牌效應."},{"pid":"1cfab20e490f6bf3ea4b05e9a9882a1a8de03fad","tid":1269119,"uid":224630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:21:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8b0c9334a646995f8b13a7be1428cd058c2e359c","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5dd0894c638f8e3ea453b08e9e3da2599d992043","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ec0e1a56d816b9b6ff2bb32ea04c976712d108c","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8393810f0fbac88f4501d0052ab819b6929f172","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"484df9c4c5e3275e0694fd09700274074732b58c","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"1c90139dba03ff08e900693bbce27eb2dae2d3ab","tid":1269119,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"推"}]}